    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this atmospheric first person horror game you step into the shoes of a caregiver, assigned yet another contract.   <br>This time to watch over Mr. Graves, an elderly man living in his isolated mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/1a8c5938dd78f68e9b9e6d667c56ef7f.poster.avif?t=1752221682\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/1a8c5938dd78f68e9b9e6d667c56ef7f.webm?t=1752221682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/1a8c5938dd78f68e9b9e6d667c56ef7f.mp4?t=1752221682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What begins as a simple job, starts to turn into something far from the ordinary. Be careful with your actions as they will shape the outcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/2b917e783c9f58092f3f62b9954a0598.poster.avif?t=1752221682\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/2b917e783c9f58092f3f62b9954a0598.webm?t=1752221682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/2b917e783c9f58092f3f62b9954a0598.mp4?t=1752221682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the eerie incidents that happened on the estate, solve puzzles and be observant to find out the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/3893378cb2fe07a2638f50ff8e2f67d2.poster.avif?t=1752221682\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/3893378cb2fe07a2638f50ff8e2f67d2.webm?t=1752221682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231740/extras/3893378cb2fe07a2638f50ff8e2f67d2.mp4?t=1752221682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixelated Retro look </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3+ hours of content with multiple endings</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >dynamic dialogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Immersive puzzles</p></li></ul>",
